    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7612054/" class="title-link">历史的触感</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7612054"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/earth1216/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1866982-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/earth1216/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">earth1216</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-09-29"
      class="main-meta">2015-09-29 20:39:30</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7612054_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我们今天的人读历史，特别是秦汉时代的历史，大都隔着一重雾。常常不自觉的带着不平和的眼光看待历史人物，于是贤者愈贤，恶者更恶。所谓“纣之不善，不如是之甚也。是以君子恶居下流，天下之恶皆归焉。”历史真的就如此吗？无非是看待历史的角度不同，立场的不同则取决与现实...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7612054_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7612054_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



